patthana8.56:1.1_0: Kilesavippayuttaṁ nasaṅkilesikaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca kilesavippayutto nasaṅkilesiko dhammo
patthana8.56:1.1_1: uppajjati hetupaccayā. Kilesavippayuttaṁ nasaṅkilesikaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca kilesavippayutto
patthana8.56:1.1_2: naasaṅkilesiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Kilesavippayuttaṁ nasaṅkilesikaṁ dhammaṁ
patthana8.56:1.1_3: paṭicca kilesavippayutto nasaṅkilesiko ca kilesavippayutto naasaṅkilesiko ca dhammā
patthana8.56:2.1: Kilesavippayuttaṁ naasaṅkilesikaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca kilesavippayutto naasaṅkilesiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.56:3.1: Kilesavippayuttaṁ nasaṅkilesikañca kilesavippayuttaṁ naasaṅkilesikañca dhammaṁ paṭicca kilesavippayutto naasaṅkilesiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana8.56:4.1: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve …pe… avigate pañca. (Sabbattha vitthāro.)
